            <div class="faq-a">Yes at many specialty lenders. Physician/Doctor Loan products commonly extend to NPs and PAs with similar low-down structure (0-10% down), no PMI, IDR-friendly DTI treatment, and signed-contract qualifying for new-grad transitions. Maximum loan amounts are typically capped lower than MD/DO programs ($1M-$1.5M extension vs $2M+ super-jumbo for physicians). For typical NP/PA income tier of $130K-$280K, the extended product handles most purchase scenarios well.</div>
